                <h1>Understanding Background Characters in Storytelling</h1>
                <p>Background characters play an essential role in storytelling, providing depth and realism to the narrative. They help create a vibrant world and can influence the protagonist's journey without being the central focus. These characters enrich the plot with subtle dynamics and reactions that enhance emotional resonance, offering flavor and context to the main storyline.</p>
